comments: Lillard (POR) reaches in and makes contact to Edwards' (MIN) front during the drive.
Towns (MIN) wraps Anthony (POR) off ball and the contact affects his FOM.
Covington (POR) and Towns (MIN) mutually engage in marginal arm to arm contact off ball.
Jones Jr. (POR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.

Replay review of the foul on Towns (MIN) pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed successful.  Covington (POR) initiates contact with his off-arm to Towns' head and the ruling on the floor is changed to an offensive foul on Covington.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a legal position in Trent Jr.'s (POR) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the off ball screen.
Okogie (MIN) makes lower body contact with Trent Jr. (POR) that affects his jump shot attempt.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of an offensive foul is overturned to a shooting foul.  Lillard (POR) is not in the restricted area, but is not established in a legal guarding position at the time of the contact with Rubio (MIN).
Marginal contact occurs between Okogie (MIN) and Lillard (POR) as Lillard changes directions and stops short in Okogie's path during the inbound.  Okogie does not dislodge Lillard from his position.
Hood (POR) commits a take foul on Rubio (MIN).
Rubio (MIN) makes contact to Lillard's (POR) body that affects his jump shot attempt.
Lillard (POR) commits a take foul on Rubio (MIN).
Towns (MIN) and Covington (POR) briefly engage in marginal contact prior to separating during the rebound.
Hood (POR) commits a take foul on Rubio (MIN).
